---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "About Us";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
	<div class="px-8 py-4">
		<h2 class="font-bold py-2">CLUB RIDES & EVENTS</h2>

		<h3 class="font-semibold py-2">Come and join in!</h3>

		<p class="">
			Rides are provided for Club Members every Sunday. Check the Events
			page for more info. Club events include a full Time Trial Club
			Events calendar throughout the spring and summer, two Audax events
			in May and various informal social rides throughout the year. We
			organise an annual Open 25 Time Trial event. This is held at the end
			of August and club members can ride for free. RDFCC also assist and
			advise on the Wild Boar Chase which is organised by the Forest of
			Dean Lions Club. and this year will be held in September.
		</p>

		<a
			href="../joinus/"
			class="text-center my-2 inline-block rounded-full
			bg-neutral-200 px-4 pb-2 pt-2.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase
			leading-normal text-neutral-700 shadow-md transition duration-150
			ease-in-out hover:bg-neutral-300 hover:shadow-lg
			focus:bg-neutral-300 focus:shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-0
			active:bg-neutral-400 active:shadow-lg dark:bg-neutral-600
			dark:text-neutral-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-500
			dark:focus:bg-neutral-500 dark:active:bg-neutral-400"
			>Join Us!</a
		><a
			href="../history/"
			class="text-center my-2 inline-block rounded-full
		bg-neutral-200 px-4 pb-2 pt-2.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase
		leading-normal text-neutral-700 shadow-md transition duration-150
		ease-in-out hover:bg-neutral-300 hover:shadow-lg
		focus:bg-neutral-300 focus:shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-0
		active:bg-neutral-400 active:shadow-lg dark:bg-neutral-600
		dark:text-neutral-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-500
		dark:focus:bg-neutral-500 dark:active:bg-neutral-400"
			>Our History</a
		>

		<h2 class="font-bold py-2">CLUB RIDES & EVENTS</h2>

		<h3 class="font-semibold py-2" >
			You're covered!
		</h3>

		<p>
			The RDFCC are affiliated with a number of national cycling
			organisations who provide a range of basic insurance cover when
			participating in club events and rides. For further details please
			visit: British Cycling Cycling Time Trials Cycling UK ​ RDFCC
			affiliation with Cycling Time Trials provides riders with basic
			insurance at RDFCC club time trials (it is not possible to ride our
			club time trials without being a member of the RDFCC or another
			affiliated club). RDFCC membership will also allow you to ride the
			club time trials of other clubs who are also affiliated (e.g. Ross &
			District CC and Newport Phoenix), as well as Open CTT events.
		</p>

		<h2 class="font-bold py-2">DISCOUNTED CLUB KIT</h2>

		<h3 class="font-semibold py-2">Let's kit you out!</h3>

		<p>
			RDFCC currently purchase club kit from Champion System UK. The kit
			is discounted by the club in special offers when the 'club shop' is
			opened. See Ali Colquoun for more details. Club kits promote the
			club on rides and at events.
		</p>

		<h2 class="font-bold py-2">LOCAL BUSINESS DISCOUNTS</h2>

		<h3 class="font-semibold py-2">You're saving!</h3>

		<p>
			On production of a membership card members can usually hope for up
			to 10% off at the following:<p>
